    "original": "Have your man learn valuable lessons and insights from a true veteran of the trade. The knowledge imparted will result in [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Have your man learn valuable lessons and insights from a true veteran of the trade. The knowledge imparted will result in [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]+35%[/color] Experience Gain for the duration of three battles.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "aa50a8dc9a2082a6d43f8e636e0949999f8d00556fe04e2867c06d5035a5de95",
    "original": "Have your man participate in a sparring fight with experienced opponents and various fighting styles. The bruises collected and lessons learned will result in [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Have your man participate in a sparring fight with experienced opponents and various fighting styles. The bruises collected and lessons learned will result in [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]+50%[/color] Experience Gain for the next battle.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "12e3e7697dbae420d15108e3566b2e54c83687a654a6afc52a86c45ce1ca89e7",
    "original": "Have your man undergo a rigorous training regimen to shape him into a skilled fighter. The blood and sweat spent today will benefit him in the long run with [color=",
